ywood Reporter |date=January 29, 2018}}</ref>}}\n|-\n| [[Primetime Emmy Award]]\n| [[Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Writing for a Variety Special|Outstanding Writing for a Variety Special]]\n| ''John Mulaney: Kid Gorgeous at Radio City''\n| {{won}}\n| {{center|<ref name=\"EmmysBio\" />}}\n|-\n|rowspan=7 |{{center|2019}}\n| [[MTV Movie & TV Awards]]\n| [[MTV Movie Award for Best Comedic Performance|Best Comedic Performance]]\n| ''Big Mouth''\n| {{nom}}\n| {{center|<ref>{{cite news |last1=Yang |first1=Rachel |title='Avengers: Endgame,' 'Game of Thrones' Dominate MTV Movie & TV Award Nominations |url=https://variety.com/2019/film/news/avengers-endgame-game-of-thrones-rbg-lead-mtv-movie-tv-award-nominations-1203214680/ |accessdate=December 31, 2019 |work=Variety |date=May 14, 2019}}</ref>}}\n|-\n| rowspan=5 |[[Primetime Emmy Award]]s\n| Outstanding Variety Sketch Series\n| ''Documentary Now!''\n| {{nom}} \n| rowspan=5 |{{center|<ref name=\"EmmysBio\" />}}\n|-\n| rowspan=2 |Outstanding Writing for a Variety Series\n| ''Documentary Now!''\n| {{nom}} \n|-\n| rowspan=2 | ''Saturday Night Live''\n| {{nom}} \n|-\n| Outstanding Guest Actor in a Comedy Series\n| {{nom}} \n|-\n| Outstanding Original Music and Lyrics\n|rowspan=2| \"Holiday Party (I Did A Little Cocaine Tonight)\"<br/> from ''Documentary Now!'' \n| {{nom}} \n|-\n| [[Hollywood Music in Media Awards]]\n| [[Hollywood Music in Media Award for Best Original Song \u2013 TV Show/Mini Series|Best Original Song \u2013 TV Show/Mini Series]]\n| {{nom}}\n| {{center|<ref>{{cite web |title=2019 Music in Visual Media Nominations |url=https://www.hmmawards.com/2019-music-in-visual-media-nominations/ |website=Hollywood Music in Media Awards |accessdate=December 31, 2019 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191128113240/https://www.hmmawards.com/2019-music-in-visual-media-nominations/ |archivedate=November 28, 2019 |url-status=live}}</ref>}}\n|}\n\n==References==\n\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category}}